export const italianDishes = [
  {
    id: "pizza-margherita",
    title: "Pizza Margherita",
    image:
      "https://api.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/608636c956ec59063fecc3b46b4f1c7e8b0c5eff?placeholderIfAbsent=true&apiKey=b59f74ae8c9444f28ee33eff06842d33",
    price: "₹300",
    quantity: "8-inch",
    description: "Classic pizza with tomato, mozzarella, and basil",
    rating: 5,
    ingredients: ["Pizza base", "Tomato sauce", "Mozzarella", "Basil"],
    instructions: [
      "Spread sauce on base.",
      "Add cheese and basil.",
      "Bake at 220°C for 10–15 mins.",
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "pasta-alfredo",
    title: "Pasta Alfredo",
    image: "https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/pasta.jpg",
    price: "₹280",
    quantity: "1 plate",
    description: "Creamy white sauce pasta with herbs",
    rating: 4.8,
    ingredients: ["Pasta", "Cream", "Cheese", "Butter", "Herbs"],
    instructions: [
      "Boil pasta.",
      "Prepare white sauce.",
      "Mix pasta with sauce and herbs.",
    ],
  },
];
